Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.87,0:02:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Moritani, are you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.29,0:02:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm okay. Just a little bump.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.71,0:02:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,This is all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.63,0:02:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Kotoura?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.25,0:02:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Your arrest, the attack on President Mifune,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.26,0:02:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Muroto's injuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.47,0:02:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,They're all—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.05,0:02:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.05,0:02:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I have this power.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.81,0:02:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I have this disgusting power, I hurt everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.10,0:02:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,No. It's not my power that's to blame.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.81,0:02:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't exist in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.27,0:02:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.07,0:02:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,How is any of this your fault?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.32,0:03:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That psycho's hurting people, not you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.66,0:03:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Manabe told you the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.57,0:03:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, yeah, Manabe!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.28,0:03:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is he missing {\i1}now{\i0} of all times?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.62,0:03:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Don't call Manabe!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.58,0:03:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You still haven't gotten over your fight with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.88,0:03:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.59,0:03:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Even after the fight, he still...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.59,0:03:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kotoura is such a klutz.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.92,0:03:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please don't let her do anything too reckless.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.01,0:03:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Screw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.80,0:03:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's got me so worried about her, I can't even eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.30,0:03:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why can't they just catch that damn criminal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.14,0:03:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then Kotoura won't do anything dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.89,0:03:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,He still kept on worrying about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.19,0:03:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Selfish, stupid me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.86,0:03:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Constantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.23,0:03:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I just can't let him get hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.36,0:03:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Kotoura.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.07,0:03:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, President Mifune. Muroto. Moritani.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.79,0:03:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry, Manabe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.08,0:03:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,For the love of—! Why is it always like this with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.63,0:03:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, what {\i1}now{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.79,0:03:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap! My parents!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.50,0:03:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.38,0:04:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. What? Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.26,0:04:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that. I'm not a little kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.31,0:04:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Pick up miso and soy sauce on the way home?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.64,0:04:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You seriously called just to give me errands?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.40,0:04:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.98,0:04:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Kotoura—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.40,0:04:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And she's gone. Why does this {\i1}always{\i0} happen to me!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.57,0:04:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope, can't do it anymore. Gonna get angry now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.72,0:04:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the park I came to with Tsukino.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.11,0:05:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Kotoura?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.90,0:05:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.65,0:05:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We keep on running into each other, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.66,0:05:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsukino.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.62,0:05:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.91,0:05:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! You're hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.62,0:05:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.80,0:05:27.26,Chalkbaofaura,,0,0,0,,{\pos(914,389)\blur0.6\fnSwis721 Md BT\fs27\frz20.18\fax-0.03\c&HE3D8CB&}Checking for new messages...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.26,0:05:28.43,Chalkbaofaura,,0,0,0,,{\pos(914,389)\blur0.6\fnSwis721 Md BT\fs27\frz20.18\fax-0.03\c&HE3D8CB&}No new messages.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.72,0:05:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.72,0:05:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,How long is this going to keep up?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.35,0:05:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll never get through that thick head of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.73,0:05:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\i1}I hate you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.69,0:05:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,She hates me, she says.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.78,0:05:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But I never thought she'd actually {\i1}want{\i0} to use her power.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.66,0:05:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It could put her in real danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.24,0:05:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did I go wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.12,0:05:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, who is it at this hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.79,0:06:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! Nobody's home today!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.71,0:06:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep it down! What time do you think—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.46,0:06:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.88,0:06:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.14,0:06:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm real sorry for the mess, but come on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.72,0:06:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,First we need to take care of that leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.35,0:06:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.23,0:06:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, all patched up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.61,0:06:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.49,0:06:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,No police officer could ignore an injured schoolgirl
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.45,0:06:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,crying alone in the dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.74,0:06:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, shall we have some dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.75,0:06:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Just you sit tight and I'll whip something up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.83,0:06:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I should text Moritani.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.21,0:06:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure she's worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.30,0:06:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm at Tsukino's apartment. Everything's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.72,0:06:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for running off on you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.14,0:06:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Send.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.73,0:06:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.36,0:07:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.69,0:07:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth is, I can't cook to save my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.74,0:07:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, shall I make something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.07,0:07:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You can cook? Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.54,0:07:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,S-So, am I being taken away for execution?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.04,0:07:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This sure brings back some memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.92,0:07:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it's only been three years
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.54,0:07:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,since we graduated from this elementary school.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.96,0:07:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is where you're going to slaughter me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.13,0:07:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That psycho attacked President Mifune.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.59,0:07:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.47,0:07:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. She's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.10,0:07:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Muroto shielded her. Thankfully he wasn't hurt too badly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.68,0:07:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Phew. That's a relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.14,0:07:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! What about Kotoura? And are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.48,0:07:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? S-Sure, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.07,0:07:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just fine. Kotoura, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.32,0:07:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make her an afterthought!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.66,0:07:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But Kotoura's run away again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.49,0:07:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,She feels my arrest,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.29,0:08:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,the attack on President Mifune,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.00,0:08:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and Muroto's injuries were all her responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.42,0:08:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it, she's thinking like that again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.30,0:08:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does that moron always assume that everything is her fault?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.51,0:08:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's how she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.63,0:08:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You must remember. You told me that yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.10,0:08:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's never once asked me for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.18,0:08:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\i1}She locked all her pain away inside herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.77,0:08:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And you, her knight—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.40,0:08:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Sulking in your room! What the hell are you thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.32,0:08:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow! What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.53,0:08:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I'm asking {\i1}you{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.95,0:08:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Why weren't you there when Kotoura was in danger?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.57,0:08:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you abandon her over a petty argument?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.62,0:08:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree, she can be completely infuriating.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.12,0:08:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's exactly why
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.50,0:08:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,you have a duty to stay with her, no matter what happens!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.17,0:08:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all Kotoura needs!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.17,0:08:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll stay with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.55,0:08:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\i1}No matter what happens, I won't leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.51,0:08:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.68,0:09:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,How could I have forgotten my most fundamental promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.81,0:09:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Manabe, can I tell you something embarrassing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.18,0:09:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.60,0:09:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you, Manabe.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.73,0:09:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh please. This is no time for joking aro—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.45,0:09:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always, always loved you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.04,0:09:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. Kotoura has all my love.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.21,0:09:32.30,Honesty,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}I looked upon the evening sky
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.04,0:09:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't reciprocate your feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.80,0:09:38.01,Honesty,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}and saw a tiny, stray cloud
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.13,0:09:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.80,0:09:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Aww, I got turned down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.64,0:09:43.64,Honesty,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}It flew slowly through the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.84,0:09:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,This might sound weird after that confession,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.85,0:09:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,but seeing you and Kotoura just feels so right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.27,0:09:49.61,Honesty,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}and reminded me about myself
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.02,0:09:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I love watching you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.48,0:09:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Moritani.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.52,0:09:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Even when you were fighting,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.78,0:09:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)}I couldn't bring myself see it as my chance. I was just worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.03,0:09:59.74,Honesty,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}I can't get hurt if I'm alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.36,0:09:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure why,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.03,0:10:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,but it really bothers me when you two aren't together.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.37,0:10:08.21,Honesty,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}I promised to never cry again
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.16,0:10:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.41,0:10:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Go and get her, right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.08,0:10:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.62,0:10:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? How should I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.96,0:10:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Find her yourself, lover boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.75,0:10:22.10,Honesty,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}But ever since I met you, both the world's colors and form seem to have changed
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.67,0:10:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.38,0:10:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Kotoura!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.71,0:10:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Moritani.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.72,0:10:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.55,0:10:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Back when you were bullying Kotoura...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.26,0:10:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad((0,500)\i1)}Kotoura looked into you, and what she saw was so foul it made her retch.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.39,0:10:28.14,Honesty,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}So I'm sure I'll be able to laugh tomorrow once again
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.31,0:10:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't have said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.18,0:10:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I've felt guilty about it this whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.19,0:10:33.02,Honesty,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}As long as I keep being honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.81,0:10:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you digging up ancient history?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.48,0:10:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And anyway you were even more horrible to me after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.36,0:10:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You said I was a bug.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.82,0:10:39.78,Honesty,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}As long as I keep being honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.86,0:10:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.00,0:10:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, enough of the teasing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.54,0:10:53.88,Honesty,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}I once drew a map of my future with crayons
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.42,0:10:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd better send him Kotoura's text.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.96,0:10:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So your family owns a dojo?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.30,0:11:00.01,Honesty,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,500)\blur1}But crumpled it up and threw it away telling myself it won't come true anyway
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.38,0:10:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.05,0:11:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\i1}Wow! That's so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.05,0:11:01.51,Chalkbaofaura,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1115,872)\blur0.6\fnSwis721 Md BT\fs54\frz18.39\c&H91887D&\fax0.02}Manabe Yoshihisa
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.09,0:11:05.31,Honesty,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}I had the feeling that even if I pursued my dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.97,0:11:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.51,0:11:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it would end this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.68,0:11:11.44,Honesty,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}and kept reaching out to them, they'd just drift away
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.47,0:11:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I {\i1}knew{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.52,0:11:21.53,Honesty,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}Something inside of me was breaking
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.40,0:11:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Muroto?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.78,0:11:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Have you been crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.20,0:11:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.16,0:11:30.16,Honesty,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}but I just ran away without being able to cope with it all alone
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.49,0:11:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, good. Looks like you're okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.41,0:11:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you "oh, good" me!\N{\alpha&HFF&}..{\r}What possessed you to go and...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.12,0:11:43.51,Honesty,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}But ever since I met you, both the world's winds and light seem to have changed
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.96,0:11:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. Everything was my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.71,0:11:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Not just what happened to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.71,0:11:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If anything had gone wrong, Kotoura and Moritani
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.30,0:11:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,might also have been victims of my selfish quest for vindication.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.80,0:11:49.73,Honesty,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}So I'm sure I'll be able to become stronger tomorrow once again
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.47,0:11:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.10,0:11:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so scared you'd never open your eyes again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.77,0:11:54.19,Honesty,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}As long as I keep being myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.10,0:11:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so scared you'd leave me like my mother did.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.36,0:12:00.78,Honesty,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}As long as I keep being myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.53,0:12:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do anything like this again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.57,0:12:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't bear to see you get hurt on my account!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.49,0:12:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't I tell you to stay home like all\Nuntrustworthy kids are supposed to?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.66,0:12:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let us see you at school again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.21,0:12:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Let her be!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.33,0:12:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.88,0:12:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a real pain in the ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.38,0:12:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.55,0:12:35.23,Honesty,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}I didn't expect my spilled tears to form a rainbow in the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.43,0:12:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1000)}Shall we head home, Mifune?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.93,0:12:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.64,0:12:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Pleading with me will only make the next time harder.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.44,0:12:40.99,Honesty,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}As I walked beside you
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.98,0:12:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Because not matter how many times it happens, I'll keep on doing the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.27,0:12:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You've always been like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.11,0:12:45.36,Honesty,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}Holding your hand
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.65,0:12:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you so damn set on protecting me even when it hurts you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.11,0:12:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I'm Mifune Chizuru's daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.41,0:12:57.84,Honesty,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}Ever since I met you, both the world's colors and form seem to have changed
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.91,0:12:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I certainly do respect your mother's legacy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.25,0:12:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But if I had to choose between her and you, I'd choose you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.67,0:12:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.08,0:13:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm saying you're more important to me than your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.13,0:13:03.92,Honesty,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}So I'm sure I'll be able to laugh tomorrow once again
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.88,0:13:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't tell you to leave off anger, or to lay aside your revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.97,0:13:08.47,Honesty,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}As long as I keep being honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.18,0:13:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But I couldn't bear to see you sacrifice the joy you have now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.56,0:13:14.14,Honesty,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}As long as I keep being honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.47,0:13:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Joy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.64,0:13:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.77,0:13:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You look so happy when you're with Kotoura and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.27,0:13:21.23,Honesty,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}As long as I keep being honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.02,0:13:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Like you've forgotten all your cares and burdens.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.23,0:13:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But. I've always lived to avenge my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.20,0:13:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We're in the same boat now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.87,0:13:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll stay with you until we reach port.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.74,0:13:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how selfish you may be, or how risible your overacting may become.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.66,0:13:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, risible?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.04,0:13:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll use any means to achieve my objectives.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.67,0:13:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the kind of person I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.89,0:13:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Kotoura, won't you marry me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.06,0:13:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid that's not really feasible.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.14,0:13:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Too bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.69,0:13:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, now that we're all full—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.23,0:14:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,is it true that the criminal knew your club president's name?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.86,0:14:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.94,0:14:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Any idea how?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.95,0:14:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. I'll discuss it with Yama tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.74,0:14:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You can stay here for tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.79,0:14:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But wouldn't I be a bother?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.50,0:14:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What did I tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.66,0:14:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No police officer would turn a blind eye to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.29,0:14:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. I do appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.05,0:14:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry again for the mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.13,0:14:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty much no one comes here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.76,0:14:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I may have a big body, but I've always been pretty timid.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.14,0:14:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone bullied me when I was a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.52,0:14:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I got tired of it, started training, and got really strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.57,0:14:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But that just scared people off.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.78,0:14:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I still wound up alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.28,0:14:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,So in the end, I used that strength to become a detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.95,0:14:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She sounds a little like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.62,0:15:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're so lucky, Kotoura.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.12,0:15:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You have friends in spite of your power.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.34,0:15:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, leave the cleaning to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.63,0:15:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You just make yourself at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.55,0:15:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.97,0:15:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She may be ditzy and blunt, but she's not a bad person.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.31,0:15:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Still, I feel a little sorry for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.31,0:15:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Something smells fishy here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.52,0:15:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Fishy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.15,0:15:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The place we ran into the random attacker
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.69,0:15:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,was the exact spot from which that detective warned us away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.28,0:15:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What's so fishy about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.36,0:15:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Telling people a place is forbidden generally just makes them more curious.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.08,0:15:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, sorry to be curious.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.79,0:15:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something else too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.12,0:15:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The criminal knew your name and where you'd be.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.17,0:15:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,There was only one person with all that information.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.92,0:15:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The daughter of Mifune Chizuru.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.05,0:15:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.43,0:15:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The clairvoyant's daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.22,0:15:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What did she want?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.43,0:15:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She warned us to stay away from the alleyway off 2nd Street. It's not safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.69,0:16:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The text Moritani forwarded me earlier said...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.77,0:16:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Kotoura's at that detective's place right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.19,0:16:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuriko!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.40,0:16:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.32,0:16:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? It's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.74,0:16:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,How did it get over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.87,0:16:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I missed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.04,0:16:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsukino.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.04,0:16:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.71,0:16:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, don't give me that look.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.76,0:16:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Haven't you been chasing me this whole time?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.14,0:16:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean, you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.14,0:16:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Bingo! I'm the criminal!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.14,0:16:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate looking at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.10,0:16:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That mind-reading is a real nuisance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.19,0:16:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll crush you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.49,0:16:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.53,0:16:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You think you can escape {\i1}me{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.32,0:16:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.95,0:17:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't understand why this is happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.25,0:17:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet people call you a klutz, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.54,0:17:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, you're trying to escape by going {\i1}up{\i0} the stairs?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.63,0:17:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}President Mifune! Muroto! Moritani!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.42,0:17:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Manabe!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.93,0:17:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Kotoura?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.43,0:17:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Did something happen, Manabe?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.97,0:17:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,No, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.51,0:17:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,More importantly, haven't you found that detective's address yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.68,0:17:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The police said it was too dangerous to tell us,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.10,0:17:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,so Muroto's looking for it right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.90,0:17:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.31,0:17:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.36,0:17:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you gonna do if we're too late?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.44,0:17:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you, Kotoura?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.28,0:17:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.12,0:17:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you attack those people?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.20,0:17:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would you want to hurt anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.66,0:17:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,To let off some steam.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.71,0:17:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,When you were talking to this woman earlier, didn't you wonder
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.38,0:17:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,why she was constantly laughing like a silly cow?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.47,0:17:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,She's always been a spineless coward,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.68,0:18:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,so she crammed all the resentment she couldn't express into the recesses of her soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.31,0:18:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's how I was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.60,0:18:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Jealous of those who seem happy,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.73,0:18:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,hateful towards those who have friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.86,0:18:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,wishing destruction on all those who enjoy the things she can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.45,0:18:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And especially on those who remind her
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.36,0:18:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,of the hell she lived in as a student.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.45,0:18:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Things were that bad for her?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.25,0:18:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So all this time, I've been burning off the stress
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.00,0:18:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,she didn't even realize she had.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.13,0:18:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It was going so well until today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.92,0:18:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I never expected to encounter an inhuman monster like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.39,0:18:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, did that hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.85,0:18:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's true: a mind-reader is nothing but a disgusting monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.73,0:18:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.48,0:18:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.98,0:18:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,She smiled at you so placidly, but in her heart she hated you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.44,0:18:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess I can't blame her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.32,0:18:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,A monster who found everything that she couldn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.95,0:19:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, honestly I couldn't care less about her feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.45,0:19:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just here to have a good time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.12,0:19:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't do that if I'm caught, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.08,0:19:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,bye-bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.00,0:19:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Until very recently,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.76,0:19:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I thought the world would be better off if I'd never been.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.30,0:19:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sometimes I was sure I ought to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.43,0:19:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.85,0:19:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kotoura!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.27,0:19:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't want to die! I don't want to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.98,0:19:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want to live! I want to live!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.27,0:19:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Manabe!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.78,0:19:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.70,0:19:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you waiting, Kotoura.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.45,0:19:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Manabe!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.74,0:19:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You psycho!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.62,0:19:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. Didn't I promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.33,0:19:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll always stay with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.21,0:19:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Manabe.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.71,0:19:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, give me a fucking break!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.67,0:19:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If you won't get out of my way, I'll just have to—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.30,0:19:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsukino, stop this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.84,0:20:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I {\i1}am{\i0} a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.51,0:20:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But I met people willing to reach out to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.31,0:20:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Big damn deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.89,0:20:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,No one ever "reached out" to {\i1}her{\i0} and no one ever will!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.10,0:20:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I thought too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.69,0:20:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But I was so wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.11,0:20:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure there are people who'll stand by you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.49,0:20:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So please don't give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.03,0:20:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Kotoura!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.45,0:20:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What are you dragging your heels for?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.20,0:20:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,She's just a damn kid talking nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.75,0:20:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I can hear your voice, Tsukino.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.00,0:20:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay. Even I was able to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.80,0:20:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't finish this, they'll just call you a criminal!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.76,0:20:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll keep helping you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.89,0:20:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So stop! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.85,0:20:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.56,0:21:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to scare you like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.40,0:21:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsukino?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.99,0:21:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Kotoura!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.24,0:21:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Kotoura!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.45,0:21:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.78,0:21:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.87,0:21:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, just a little shaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.08,0:21:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Tsukino!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.92,0:21:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to answer for my crimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.30,0:21:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsukino.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.18,0:21:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So there you have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.85,0:21:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's move. In the car with ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.31,0:21:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yama.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.56,0:21:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,When you're out, look me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.69,0:21:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll treat you to some dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.19,0:21:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I get the big set?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.98,0:21:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn lug! You're only gettin' the kiddie meal!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.44,0:21:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Kotoura, let's head home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.24,0:21:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.87,0:21:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.16,0:22:05.09,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(525,300)\fsp-1.5\blur2}How do you stand again when something trips you up?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.13,0:22:17.94,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,750)\fsp-1.5\blur2}Can truth be found by thinking about the days to come?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:17.19,0:22:26.19,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(775,300)\fsp-1.5\blur2}We all come into this world alone when we are born,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.86,0:22:27.70,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\fsp-1.5\blur2}and precisely because of that,
Dialogue: 1,0:22:27.36,0:22:34.74,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\fsp-1.5\blur2}we try to live life with others from then on
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.62,0:22:43.04,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\fsp-1.5\blur2}Back then you taught me the strength to live and the meaning to it all,
Dialogue: 1,0:22:42.75,0:22:48.38,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\fsp-1.5\blur2}and I embrace it with all my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.17,0:22:54.93,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\fsp-1.5\blur2}So that in all things around us the flower of hope may bloom,
Dialogue: 1,0:22:54.64,0:23:00.73,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\fsp-1.5\blur2}we start our days together here
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.85,0:23:07.36,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,525)\fsp-1.5\blur2}We start our days together here
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.09,0:23:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,ESP Society, assemble!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.51,0:23:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Present!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.17,0:23:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We've reached the final episode,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.72,0:23:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,so let's do the last preview together!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.39,0:23:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.93,0:23:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Kotoura's erotic legend will never die!
